  "name": "Earth Release Meteor Fall",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Icons/Earth.png",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Upon completion you select 4 different points you can see within range. Each creature in a 30- foot radius sphere centered on the point you select must make a Dexterity Saving Throw against your Ninjutsu Save DC. Massive Chunks of stone earth and mud comes raining upon the selected areas. A creature takes 10d10 Bludgeoning &amp; 10d10 Earth Damage and is Dazed and knocked Prone on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one. A creature can only be affected by one meteor per casting.</p>",
